*SyScan'10 CALL FOR PAPERS*

*ABOUT SYSCAN'10*
This year, SyScan'10 will be held in the 4 exciting cities of Singapore,
Hangzhou, Taipei and Ho Chi Minh City. Details are as follows:

*/SyScan'10 Singapore
/*date: 17 – 18 June 2010

*/SyScan'10 HangZhou
/*date: 10 - 11 July 2010

*/SyScan'10 Taipei
